1 (b) Any balance in the performance fund at the close of any fiscal year shall not
2 lapse but shall be carried forward to the next fiscal year and be continuously
3 appropriated for the purposes specified in this section. A general statement
4 that all continuing appropriations are repealed, discontinued, or suspended
5 shall not operate to repeal, discontinue, or suspend this fund or to repeal this
6 action.
7 Section 2. Whereas the work of the postsecondary education working group is
8 necessary for the funding of public postsecondary education institutions, an emergency is
9 declared to exist, and this Act takes effect upon its passage and approval by the Governor
10 or upon its otherwise becoming a law.
